snippet.title: How to Control Euro Truck Simulator 2 using Android device | Fully Functional All in One Controller!
snippet.description:
Hey whats up yo guys, welcome back to another tutorial on how to control your PC games using your android device. The Monect Gaming Controller does this magic and preciously you can keep the control over the game and the Controller itself. The Steering accuracy is pretty much good and it use sensors of your android device.

Officially, there was no any gaming layout made for Euro Truck Simulator 2. So i thought it'd be great if i could design a fully functional layout myself for the addictive simulation game. So here we're!

snippet.title: Gta 5 All in One Weapons Location | Story Mode Unlimited Ammo Glitch ( PS5/4, XBox One/X, PC ) 2022
snippet.description:
Hey what's up you guys, im back with another tutorial on Gta V! So today I'm gonna show you how to find Weapons for free in Gta 5 Story Mode(offline) with the exact spawn locations that you can find underneath the sea. Also the glitch shown in the video can be used to collect unlimited ammo for the found Weapons.

You'll find almost everything you need to know upto date because im playing on the one of the latest version which is 1.57(1.58 is the most recent one) and i can ensure that these locations and methods are working across most of the platforms including ps5, ps4, ps3, xbox one, xbox series x, xbox 360 and pc(which im demonstrating).

This is what i found so far

Weapons:
‚ñ´Ô∏èAssault Riffle
‚ñ´Ô∏èSniper Riffle
‚ñ´Ô∏èSMG
‚ñ´Ô∏èPump Shotgun

‚ñ´Ô∏èSticky Bombs
‚ñ´Ô∏èGrenades

‚óΩIf you encounter sharks when reaching the location, just swim down to the bottom so the sharks will lose you eventually and leave you behind.

‚óΩSometimes, you'll find a briefcase which contains handy amount of cash even though switching characters doesn't respawn them as the glitch patched in the latest version.
